messages.content: If you're still stuck on this, my issue was that the order of the `#[instruction(...args)]` has to match the instruction args exactly. I had reversed two args accidentally so Anchor was trying to parse the bytes incorrectly. After I fixed the ordering, passing the object on the JS side worked like a charm.
